五、完成加害人處遇計畫。\r\n附件：聲請簡易判決處刑書","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/111%2c%e8%8a%b1%e7%b0%a1%2c208%2c20220905%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,111,花簡,208,20220905,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"花簡","JNO":"208","JDATE":"20220905","JTITLE":"違反家庭暴力防治法"}